Exception Handling
The application uses both predefined and user-defined exceptions to handle errors gracefully

1. InvalidBookSelectionException(User-defined): 
                    Thrown when an invalid book submodule or menu code is selected.
2. InvalidReservationSelectionException (User-defined): 
					Thrown when an invalid reservation code is selected,
3. NumberFormatException(Predefined):
 					Handles invalid numeric input.
4. InputMismatchException(Predefined): 
					Catches invalid input types, ensuring correct data types are provided.